vars = dict(OPENTAXII_DOMAIN='hostname:1337', OPENTAXII__SUPPORT_BASIC_AUTH
    ='yes', OPENTAXII__PERSISTENCE_API__CLASS='something.Else',
    OPENTAXII__PERSISTENCE_API__OTHER='1')
expected = dict(domain='hostname:1337', support_basic_auth=True,
    persistence_api={'class': 'something.Else', 'other': 1})
assert ServerConfig._get_env_config(env=vars) == expected
